g *)eai_urlParametersString:(NSDictionary *)parameters {
    if (parameters.count == 0) {
        return @"";
    }
    __block NSDictionary *parameterDict = parameters;
    __block NSMutableString *parametersString = [NSMutableString string];
    [parameterDict enumerateKeysAndObjectsUsingBlock:^(id  _Nonnull key, id  _Nonnull obj, BOOL * _Nonnull stop) {
        NSString *str = [NSString stringWithFormat:@"&%@=%@",key,obj];
        [parametersString appendString:str];
    }];
    return parametersString;
}

    override func layoutAttributesForElements(in rect: CGRect) -> [UICollectionViewLayoutAttributes]? {
        guard let attributes = super.layoutAttributesForElements(in: rect) else {
            return nil
        }

        guard let containerView = collectionView else {
            return super.layoutAttributesForElements(in: rect)
        }

        let centerX = containerView.contentOffset.x + containerView.bounds.width / 2.0
        var centerIndexPath = IndexPath(item: 0, section: 0)
        // 存放最小的间距值
        var minDelta = CGFloat.greatestFiniteMagnitude
        for attribute in attributes ?? [] {
            let delta = abs(attribute.center.x - centerX)
            if delta < minDelta {
                minDelta = delta
                centerIndexPath = attribute.indexPath
                attribute.zIndex = kMaxzIndex
            }
        }

        for attribute in attributes {
            let distance = abs(attribute.center.x - centerX)
            let distanceRate = distance / CGFloat

AITInterQAModule/AITInterQAModule/Classes/Src/Card/view/Common/ChooseMood/ChooseMoodCollectionViewFlowLayout.swift (Line 76:9 - Line 110:2), AITInterQAModule/AITInterQAModule/Classes/Src/Card/view/Common/Game/ChooseGameCollectionViewFlowLayout.swift (Line 58:9 - Line 92:2)

    override func shouldInvalidateLayout(forBoundsChange _: CGRect) -> Bool {
        return true
    }

    override func targetContentOffset(forProposedContentOffset proposedContentOffset: CGPoint, withScrollingVelocity _: CGPoint) -> CGPoint {
        let collectionViewSize: CGSize = collectionView?.bounds.size ?? CGSize(width: 0, height: 0)

        var rect = CGRect()
        rect.origin.y = 0
        rect.origin.x = proposedContentOffset.x
        rect.size = collectionViewSize

        // 获得super已经计算好的布局属性
        let attributes = super.layoutAttributesForElements(in: rect)

        // 计算collectionView最中心点的x值
        let centerX = proposedContentOffset.x + collectionViewSize.width * 0.5
        var minDelta = CGFloat.greatestFiniteMagnitude
        for attrs in attributes ?? [] {
            if abs(minDelta) > abs(attrs.center.x - centerX) {
                minDelta = attrs.center.x - centerX
            }
        }

        // 修改原有的偏移量
        var updatedProposedContentOffset = proposedContentOffset
        updatedProposedContentOffset.x += minDelta
        return updatedProposedContentOffset
    }
}

    /// 当前最上层VC为子VC的时候，获取该子VC
    private func getTopSubVCIfNeeded(of rootVC: UIViewController?) -> UIViewController? {
        guard let rootVC, !rootVC.children.isEmpty else { return rootVC }
        let topSubvc = rootVC.children.filter {
            $0.view.frame != .zero && !$0.view.isHidden
        }.last
        return topSubvc ?? rootVC
    }

    private func hollowLayout() {
        if isInactiveHollow {
            for (index, layer) in inactiveLayer.enumerated() {
                if index == currentIndex, !isActiveHollow {
                    layer.backgroundColor = activeColor.cgColor
                } else {
                    layer.backgroundColor = UIColor.clear.cgColor
                    layer.borderColor = activeColor.cgColor
                }
                layer.borderColor = activeColor.cgColor
                layer.borderWidth = 1
            }
        } else {
            for (index, layer) in inactiveLayer.enumerated() {
                if index == currentIndex {
                    layer.backgroundColor = activeColor.cgColor
                } else {
                    layer.backgroundColor = inactiveColor.cgColor
                }
                layer.borderWidth = 0
            }
        }
    }

struct CornerRadii {
        var topLeft: CGFloat = 0
        var topRight: CGFloat = 0
        var bottomLeft: CGFloat = 0

            self.topRight = topRight
            self.bottomLeft = bottomLeft
            self.bottomRight = bottomRight

func addCorner(cornerRadii: CornerRadii, size: CGSize, borderColor: UIColor, borderWidth: CGFloat, bgColor: UIColor) -> AddedLayer {
        let rect = CGRect(origin: CGPoint(x: 0, y: 0), size: size)
        let path = createPathWithRoundedRect(bounds: rect, cornerRadii: cornerRadii)
        let shapLayer = CAShapeLayer()
        shapLayer.frame = rect
        shapLayer.path = path

        // 设置边框
        let borderLayer = CAShapeLayer()
        borderLayer.path = path
        borderLayer.fillColor = bgColor.cgColor
        borderLayer.strokeColor = borderColor.cgColor
        borderLayer.lineWidth = borderWidth
        borderLayer.frame = rect
        borderLayer.mask = shapLayer
        base

AITSwiftPlatformModule/AITSwiftPlatformModule/Classes/Src/HLMKit/UIKit/UIView+HLMAdditions.swift (Line 192:2 - Line 244:2), AITSwiftPlatformModule/AITSwiftPlatformModule/Classes/Src/Util/Extension/UIView+Extension.swift (Line 196:5 - Line 248:2)

func createPathWithRoundedRect(bounds: CGRect, cornerRadii: CornerRadii) -> CGPath {
        let minX = bounds.minX
        let minY = bounds.minY
        let maxX = bounds.maxX
        let maxY = bounds.maxY

        let topLeftCenterX = minX + cornerRadii.topLeft
        let topLeftCenterY = minY + cornerRadii.topLeft

        let topRightCenterX = maxX - cornerRadii.topRight
        let topRightCenterY = minY + cornerRadii.topRight

        let bottomLeftCenterX = minX + cornerRadii.bottomLeft
        let bottomLeftCenterY = maxY - cornerRadii.bottomLeft

        let bottomRightCenterX = maxX - cornerRadii.bottomRight
        let bottomRightCenterY = maxY - cornerRadii.bottomRight

        let path = CGMutablePath()
        // 顶左
        path.addArc(center: CGPoint(x: topLeftCenterX, y: topLeftCenterY), radius: cornerRadii.topLeft, startAngle: CGFloat.pi, endAngle: CGFloat.pi * 3 / 2, clockwise: false)
        // 顶右
        path.addArc(center: CGPoint(x: topRightCenterX, y: topRightCenterY), radius: cornerRadii.topRight, startAngle: CGFloat.pi * 3 / 2, endAngle: 0, clockwise: false)
        // 底右
        path.addArc(center: CGPoint(x: bottomRightCenterX, y: bottomRightCenterY), radius: cornerRadii.bottomRight, startAngle: 0, endAngle: CGFloat.pi / 2, clockwise: false)
        // 底左
        path.addArc(center: CGPoint(x: bottomLeftCenterX, y: bottomLeftCenterY), radius: cornerRadii.bottomLeft, startAngle: CGFloat.pi / 2, endAngle: CGFloat.pi, clockwise: false)
        path.closeSubpath()
        return path
    }

    func imageFromColor(color: UIColor, viewSize: CGSize) -> UIImage {
        let rect = CGRect(x: 0, y: 0, width: viewSize.width, height: viewSize.height)
        if rect.size.width <= 0 || rect.size.height <= 0 {
            assertionFailure("rect.size exception")
            return UIImage()
        }
        UIGraphicsBeginImageContext(rect.size)
        guard let context = UIGraphicsGetCurrentContext() else {
            assertionFailure("UIGraphicsGetCurrentContext()为nil")
            return UIImage()
        }
        context.setFillColor(color.cgColor)
        context.fill(rect)
        guard let image = UIGraphicsGetImageFromCurrentImageContext() else {
            assertionFailure("UIGraphicsGetImageFromCurrentImageContext()为nil")
            return UIImage()
        }
        UIGraphicsEndImageContext()
        return image
    }

    @objc
    func backwardClick(_ sender: AnyObject) {
        guard endPos > 0 else { return }
        self.endPos = endPos - 1
        sliderBar.value = Float(endPos)
        renderToCurrentPos()
        progressLabel.text = "\(endPos)\\\(textLength)"
        if toolBarState_autoStream {
            endStreamText(sender)
        }
    }
    
    @objc
    func forwardClick(_ sender: AnyObject) {
        guard endPos < textLength else { return }
        self.endPos = endPos + 1
        sliderBar.value = Float(endPos)
        renderToCurrentPos()
        progressLabel.text = "\(endPos)\\\(textLength)"
        if toolBarState_autoStream {
            endStreamText(sender)
        }
    }
    
    private var streamingCanceller: TimeDelay.Canceller?
    
    @objc
    func openMessageInterruptedState(_ sender: AnyObject) {
        toolBarState_interrupted = true
    }
    
    @objc
    func closeMessageInterruptedState(_ sender: AnyObject) {
        toolBarState_interrupted = false
    }
    
    @objc
    func showLastGlypha(_ sender: AnyObject) {
        toolBarState_showLastGlyph = true
    }
    
    @objc
    func hideLastGlypha(_ sender: AnyObject) {
        toolBarState_showLastGlyph = false
    }
    
    @objc
    func startStreamText(_ sender: AnyObject) {
        guard endPos < textLength else {
            return
        }
        toolBarState_autoStream = true
        streamingAtIndex(endPos + 1)
    }
    
    @objc
    func endStreamText(_ sender: AnyObject) {
        if let canceller = streamingCanceller {
            canceller.cancel()
            streamingCanceller = nil
        }
        toolBarState_autoStream = false
    }
    
    @objc
    func currentPosChanged(_ sender: UIControl) {
        let pos = max(0, min(textLength, Int(sliderBar.value)))
        self.endPos = pos
        sliderBar.value = Float(pos)
        renderToCurrentPos()
        progressLabel.text = "\(endPos)\\\(textLength)"
    }

        let text

    func streamingAtIndex(_ index: Int) {
        if index > textLength, endPos == textLength {
            endStreamText(self)
            return
        }
        endPos = min(index, textLength)
        sliderBar.value = Float(endPos)
        currentPosChanged(sliderBar)
        
        streamingCanceller = TimeDelay.delay(0.04) { [weak self] in
            self?.streamingAtIndex(index + 1)
        }
    }
    
    func updateLastGlyphView() {
        if let rect = markdownView.lastGlyphRect() {
            lastGlyphView.backgroundColor = UIColor.red.withAlphaComponent(0.4)
            lastGlyphView.frame = rect
        } else {
            lastGlyphView.backgroundColor = UIColor.green.withAlphaComponent(0.4)
        }
    }

func contextMenuInteraction(_ interaction: UIContextMenuInteraction, configurationForMenuAtLocation location: CGPoint) -> UIContextMenuConfiguration? {
        let _debugClick = { [weak self] in
            self?.debugClick?()
        }
        return UIContextMenuConfiguration(identifier: nil, previewProvider: nil, actionProvider: { _ in
            var children: [UIMenuElement] = []
            children.append(UIAction(
                title: FlowMdManager.provideText(forKey: .longPressCopy) ?? "",
                image: UIImage(systemName: "doc.on.doc")
            ) { _ in
                if let text = self.markdownString, !text.isEmpty {
                    UIPasteboard.general.string = text
                }
            })
            if let name = FlowMdManager.debugMenuItemName {
                let element = UIAction(
                    title: name,
                    image: UIImage(systemName: "arrow.up.square")
                ) { _ in
                    _debugClick()
                }
                children.append(element)
            }
            return UIMenu(title: "", children: children)
        })
    }

func refresh(withFeedList: [CollectionCellModelProtocol]) {
        loadingView.isHidden = true
        
        collectionViewSection.removeAll()
        collectionViewSection.append(items: withFeedList)
        
        if collectionViewManager.sections.count <= 0 {
            collectionViewManager.append(section: collectionViewSection)
        }
        collectionViewManager.reloadData()
        
        collectionView.mj_header?.endRefreshing()

        if !hasMore {
            loadMoreFooter.setState(state: .NoMoreData)
            collectionView.mj_footer?.endRefreshingWithNoMoreData()
        }
    }

func toVideoModel() -> TTVideoEngineModel? {
        guard let jsonData = data(using: .utf8, allowLossyConversion: true) else {
            return nil
        }

        guard
            let dictionary = try? JSONSerialization.jsonObject(with: jsonData,
                                                               options: .allowFragments) as? [AnyHashable: Any]
        else {
            return nil
        }

        return TTVideoEngineModel.videoModel(withDict: dictionary)
    }

    func keyboardShow(_ noti: Notification) {

        }
    }

    func initSplitY() {

        splitYMax = max(splitYMax, splitYMid + 1.0)

        }
        splitYOnEndMaxDict[splitYOnEndList[splitYOnEndList.count - 1]] = CGFloat.infinity
        splitY

    func onGestureContainerPan(_ pan: UIPanGestureRecognizer) {
        let point = pan.translation(in: nil)
        func beginHandler() {
            originPanX = point.x
            originPanY = point.y
            lastPanX = point.x
            lastPanY = point.y
            panLastTime = Date().timeIntervalSince1970
        }
        if pan.state == .began {
            self.originTouchPoint = pan.location(in: splitView)
        }
        
        // 子视图可以滑动, 由于isCvScrollEnable会中断subview的panGesture顾暂不考虑top的情况
        let isSplitViewTouched = isTouchInHeaderSplitView()
        if !isSplitViewTouched, cvScrollState == .scrollable, splitY == splitYMin {
            disableCount += 1
            return
        }
        // disableCount用于标记多手势处理过程中的状态重置，第一次进入到这里的时候重置手指坐标，和begin的逻辑一样
        if disableCount != 0 {
            beginHandler()
            disableCount = 0
        }
        
        if pan.state == .began {
            panEnableWhenBegan = panEnable
        }
        if !panEnableWhenBegan {
            return
        }
        switch pan.state {
        case .began:
            beginHandler()
        case .changed:
            if !isPanHorizontal, !isPanVertical {
                if abs(originPanX - point.x) > abs(originPanY - point.y) {
                    isPanHorizontal = true
                } else {
                    isPanVertical = true
                }
            }
            let dy: CGFloat = isPanVertical ? (point.y - lastPanY) : dyBy(dx: point.x - lastPanX)
            onPanMainSplit(withDeltaY: dy)
            panSpeedY = dy / max(0.001, (Date().timeIntervalSince1970 - panLastTime))
            lastPanX = point.x
            lastPanY = point.y
            panLastTime = Date().timeIntervalSince1970
            dealWithGuideEntrance(resetY: true)
        case .ended:
            let dy: CGFloat = isPanVertical ? (point.y - lastPanY) : dyBy(dx: point.x - lastPanX)
            onPanMainSplit(withDeltaY: dy)
            onPanMainSplitEnd(speedY: panSpeedY)
            resetPanVarieties()
            dealWithGuideEntrance(resetY: true)
        @unknown default:
            onPanMainSplitEnd()
            resetPanVarieties()
        }
    }
    
    /// 手指是否在顶部tabbar上滑动
    private func isTouchInHeaderSplitView() -> Bool {
        let hotBounds = CGRect(x: 0,
                               y: -10,
                               width: splitView.bounds.size.width,
                               height: splitView.bounds.size.height + 20) // 扩大热区
        let hitted = hotBounds.contains(originTouchPoint)
        return hitted
    }
    
    func dyBy(dx: CGFloat) -> CGFloat{
        if dx <= 0 {
            return 0
        }
        return dx * (splitYMax - splitYMin) / max(1.0, UIScreen.main.bounds.width * 0.5)
    }

    func resetPanVarieties() {
        isPanHorizontal = false
        isPanVertical = false
        originPanX = 0.0
        originPanY = 0.0
        lastPanX = 0.0
        lastPanY = 0.0
        panLastTime = 0.0
        panSpeedY = 0.0
    }

    func onPanMainSplit(expectedPos pos: CGFloat) {
        if !panEnable {
            return
        }
        splitYExpected = pos
        onPanMainSplit()
    }

    func onPanMainSplit(withDeltaY dy: CGFloat) {
        if !panEnable {
            return
        }
        splitYExpected += dy
        onPanMainSplit()
    }

    private func onPanMainSplit() {
        splitY = min(max(splitYExpected, splitYMin), splitYMax)
        layoutViews()
    }
    
    func stopScrollAnimate() {
        scrollAnimate?.stop()
        scrollAnimate = nil
    }

    func scrollSplitWithAnimate(to sY: CGFloat) {
        resetEntranceViewIfNeeded(to: sY)
        stopScrollAnimate()
        // 如果开始时位置已接近终点则不需要做动画
        if abs(sY - splitY) < 1.0 {
            splitYExpected = sY
            splitY = splitYExpected
            layoutViews()
            return
        }
        // 根据移动距离改变动画时间
        var duration = (abs(splitY - sY) / max(1.0, (splitYMax - splitYMin)) * 0.5 * 5)
        duration = max(0.1, min(0.5, duration))
        let interpolator = AITEaseCubicInterpolator(time: CAMediaTimingFunction(name: .easeInEaseOut), accuracy: 100)
        scrollAnimate = AITValueAnimator(duration: duration, startValue: splitY, endValue: sY, interpolator: interpolator, delegate: self)
        scrollAnimate

    func onPanMainSplitEnd(speedY: CGFloat = 0.0) {
        for splitYOnEnd in splitYOnEndList {
            let splitYOnEndMax = splitYOnEndMaxDict[splitYOnEnd] ?? view.height
            if splitY + speedY * 0.15 < splitYOnEndMax {
                notifyHeaderViewVisableChange(targetSplitY: splitYOnEnd)
                scrollSplitWithAnimate(to: splitYOnEnd)
                return
            }
        }
    }

    func showGuideEntranceAnimation() {

        self.guideEntranceView.isHidden = false
        self.guideEntrancePosY = self.view.height - AITSearchResultQaBottomView.calcHeight() - 78 - 72
        UIView.animate(withDuration: 0.2) { [weak self] in

            self.guideEntranceView.frame = CGRect(x: self.guideEntranceView.origin.x, y:  self.guideEntrancePosY, width: self.guideEntranceView.btd_width, height: self.guideEntranceView.btd_height)
            self.guideEntranceView.alpha = 1.0
        } completion: { [weak self] _ in
            guard let self = self else { return }
            self.guideEntranceView.isHidden = false
            self.isGuideEntranceAnimating = false
        }

    }
    
    func hideGuideEntranceAnimation() {

            self.guideEntranceView.alpha = 0.0
        } completion: { [weak self] _ in
            guard let self = self else { return }
            self.guideEntranceView.isHidden = true
            self.isGuideEntranceAnimating = false
        }
    }

            return
        }
        view.addDoubleTapAction { [weak self, weak view] _ in
            guard let self = self, let view = view else { return }

        }
    }

            let pasteboard = UIPasteboard.general
            pasteboard.string = str

        }
        toolTip.show()
    }

    override func keyboardShow(_ noti: Notification) {
        super.keyboardShow(noti)

        let info = noti.userInfo
        if let kbRect = (info?[UIResponder.keyboardFrameEndUserInfoKey] as? NSValue)?.cgRectValue {
            guard let window = UIApplication.shared.delegate?.window else {
                return
            }
            updateCollectionBottom(bottom: inputBar.btd_height + kbRect.height)
            vm.needScrollToBottom(animate: false)
            inputBar.keyboardShow(kbRect)
        }
    }

        super.keyboardHide(noti)
        inputBar.keyboardHide()
        updateCollectionBottom(bottom: collectionBottom)
    }

, execute: task)
            }
        case .denied:
            showAlert()
        default:
            break
        }
    }
    
    override func touchesMoved(_ touches: Set<UITouch>, with event: UIEvent?) {
        if !isVoiceMode() || !isVoiceInputStart {
            super.touchesMoved(touches, with: event)
            return
        }
        if let touch = touches.first {
            let location = touch.location(in: self)
            updateVoiceInputStatus(isTouchOutside(location))
        }
    }
    
    override func touchesEnded(_ touches: Set<UITouch>, with event: UIEvent?) {
        if !isVoiceMode() || !isVoiceInputStart {
            cancelTask()
            super.touchesEnded(touches, with: event)
            return
        }
        if let touch = touches.first {
            let location = touch.location(in: self)
            if isTouchOutside(location) {
                cancelVoiceInput()
            } else {
                stopVoiceInput()
            }
        }
    }
    
    override func touchesCancelled(_ touches: Set<UITouch>, with event: UIEvent?) {
        if !isVoiceMode() || !isVoiceInputStart {
            cancelTask()
            super.touchesCancelled(touches, with: event)
            return
        }
        if let touch = touches.first {
            let location = touch.location(in: self)
            if isTouchOutside(location) {
                cancelVoiceInput()
            } else {
                stopVoiceInput()
            }
        }
    }

    func show(from view: UIView, with faq: HippoApiCommonQuestionSearchCommonFaqBubble?, selectText: String) {

            grayView?.removeFromSuperview()
        }
        sendCompletion = { [weak self, weak grayView, weak faqView] in
            grayView?.removeFromSuperview()
        }
    }

    override func keyboardShow(_ noti: Notification) {
        super.keyboardShow(noti)

        let info = noti.userInfo
        if let kbRect = (info?[UIResponder.keyboardFrameEndUserInfoKey] as? NSValue)?.cgRectValue {
            guard let window = UIApplication.shared.delegate?.window else {
                return
            }
            updateCollectionBottom(bottom: inputBar.btd_height + kbRect.height)
            vm.needScrollToBottom(animate: false)
            inputBar.keyboardShow(kbRect)
        }
    }

    override func keyboardHide(_ noti: Notification) {
        super.keyboardHide(noti)
        inputBar.keyboardHide()
        updateCollectionBottom(bottom: collectionBottom)
    }

    override func touchesBegan(_ touches: Set<UITouch>, with _: UIEvent?) {
        if touches.first?.view?.isDescendant(of: inputBar) != true {
            view.endEditing(true)
        }
    }
    
    override func configPageStatus(status: PageStatus) {
        super.configPageStatus(status: status)
        switch status {
        case .loading:
            inputBar.isHidden = true
        case .error:
            inputBar.isHidden = true
        default:
            inputBar.isHidden = false
        }
    }

func isShowMsgFuncOrReferenceTool() -> Bool {
        let superView = BTDResponder.topViewController()?.view
        var isShow = false
        superView?.subviews.forEach { view in
            if view.tag == MsgMountReferenceViewCell.referenceToolTipsKey {
                isShow = true
                return
            }
            if view.isKind(of: MsgPopupView.self) {
                isShow = true
                return
            }
        }
        return isShow
    }

func getPublicKey() -> Promise<HippoApiTuringUserRegisterGetPublicKeyResponse> {
        return Promise<HippoApiTuringUserRegisterGetPublicKeyResponse>.init { resolve, reject in
            let request = HippoApiTuringUserRegisterGetPublicKeyRequest()
            HippoApiTuringUserApiUserApiServiceClient.getPublicKey(request: request) { [weak self] result in
                switch result {
                case .success(let response):
                    if let model = response.model {
                        self?.publicKeyResponse = model
                        resolve(model)
                    } else {
                        reject(NSError(domain: "", code: -1))
                    }
                case .failure(let error):
                    reject(error)
                }
            }
        }
    }

func getRSAEncryptValue(value: String) -> String {
        var result = ""
        if let publicKeyString = publicKeyResponse?.publicKey, let valueData = value.data(using: .utf8) {
            do {
                let data = try valueData.btd.encrypt(publicKey: publicKeyString)
                if let data = data {
                    result = data.base64EncodedString()
                }
            } catch {

            }
        }
        return result
    }

        let resetOrientationTarget = NSNumber(value: UIInterfaceOrientation.unknown.rawValue)
        UIDevice.current.setValue(resetOrientationTarget, forKey: "orientation")

        let orientationTarget = NSNumber(value: interfaceOrientation.rawValue)
        UIDevice.current.setValue(orientationTarget, forKey: "orientation")

        UIViewController.attemptRotationToDeviceOrientation()
    }

    func saveImageToAlbum(image: UIImage) {
        PHPhotoLibrary.requestAuthorization { status in
            if status == .authorized {

                    PHAssetChangeRequest.creationRequestForAsset(from: image)

    public static func checkAuthority(for mediaType: AVMediaType, completion: ((Bool) -> Void)? = nil) {
        let status = AVCaptureDevice.authorizationStatus(for: mediaType)
        switch status {
        case .authorized:
            completion?(true)
        case .notDetermined:
            AVCaptureDevice.requestAccess(for: mediaType) { success in
                completion?(success)
            }
        default:
            completion?(false)
        }
    }

extension Reactive where Base: AnyObject {
  func synchronizedBag<T>(_ action: () -> T) -> T {
    objc_sync_enter(base)
    let result = action()
    objc_sync_exit(base)
    return result
  }
}

    private func replaceAll(regex: String, to replacement: String) -> String {

let tarDate = Date(timeIntervalSince1970: timeInterval)
    let curDate = Date(timeIntervalSince1970: baseTimeInterval)
    var calendar = Calendar.current
    let tarComp = calendar.dateComponents([.year, .month, .day, .weekday], from: tarDate)
    let curComp = calendar.dateComponents([.year, .month, .day, .weekday], from: curDate)
    let tarDateOnlyDay = calendar.date(from: tarComp) ?? Date()
    let curDateOnlyDay = calendar.date(from: curComp) ?? Date()

    let formatter = DateFormatter()
    let compOnlyDay = calendar.dateComponents([.day], from: curDateOnlyDay, to: tarDateOnlyDay)
    let compDay = compOnlyDay.day ?? 0
    if compDay == 0 {
        // 同一天
        let compHourMinute = calendar.dateComponents([.hour, .minute], from: curDate, to: tarDate)
        let compHour = compHourMinute.hour ?? 0
        if compHour == 0 {
            // 相差不超过1小时
            let compMinute = compHourMinute.minute ?? 0
            if compMinute == 0 {
                // 相差不超过1分钟
                formatter.dateFormat = "刚刚"
            } else if compMinute < 0 {
                // 超过1分钟且在前
                formatter.dateFormat = "\(-compMinute)分钟前"
            } else {
                // 超过1分钟且在后
                formatter.dateFormat = "HH:mm"
            }
        } else if compHour < 0 {
            // 超过1小时且在前
            formatter.dateFormat = "\(-compHour)小时前"
        } else {
            // 超过1小时且在后
            formatter.dateFormat = "HH:mm"
        }
    } else if compDay == -1 {
        // 昨天
        formatter.dateFormat = "昨天"
    } else if tarComp

    func onTopicItemClick(cellModel: CreationTopicFloatViewCellModel?, isSelected: Bool) {
        selectedTopic = cellModel?.topic
        if let cellModel = cellModel {
            topicListView.collectionViewSection.items.forEach { model in
                if let item = model as? CreationTopicFloatViewCellModel {
                    item.isSelected = false
                }
            }
            cellModel.isSelected = isSelected
            topicListView.reloadData()
            
            listener?.onTopicItemClick(topic: cellModel.topic)
        } else {
            topicListView.collectionViewSection.items.forEach { model in
                if let item = model as? CreationTopicFloatViewCellModel {
                    item.isSelected = false
                }
            }
            topicListView.reloadData()
            listener?.onTopicItemClick(topic: nil)
        }
    }

// MARK: - Implementation Details

private func objectFromJSON<T>(at path: String) -> T {
  guard let url = getBundle().url(forResource: path, withExtension: nil),
    let json = try? JSONSerialization.jsonObject(with: Data(contentsOf: url), options: []),
    let result = json as? T else {
    fatalError("Unable to load JSON at path: \(path)")
  }
  return result
}

private struct JSONDocument {
  let data: [String: Any]

  init(path: String) {
    self.data = objectFromJSON(at: path)
  }

  subscript<T>(key: String) -> T {
    guard let result = data[key] as? T else {
      fatalError("Property '\(key)' is not of type \(T.self)")
    }
    return result
  }
}

AITStudyModule/AITStudyModule/Classes/Src/StudyFeedCell.swift (Line 145:5 - Line 165:10), AITCreationModule/AITCreationModule/Classes/Src/CreateTools/CreationNewToolListHeaderView.swift (Line 268:5 - Line 289:25)

    private func setupGradientBackground(gradientStart: String, gradientEnd: String) {
        if let oldGradientLayer = contentView.layer.sublayers?.first(where: { $0 is CAGradientLayer }) {
            oldGradientLayer.removeFromSuperlayer()
        }
        let gradientLayer = CAGradientLayer()
        gradientLayer.frame = contentView.bounds
        
        gradientLayer.colors = [ UIColor(hexString: gradientStart).cgColor,
                                 UIColor(hexString: gradientEnd).cgColor
        ]
        gradientLayer.startPoint = CGPoint(x: 0.5, y: 0.0)
        gradientLayer.endPoint = CGPoint(x: 0.5, y: 1.0)
        gradientLayer.cornerRadius = contentView.layer.cornerRadius
        gradientLayer.masksToBounds = true
        contentView.layer.insertSublayer(gradientLayer, at: 0)
    }
}

func addCornerRadiusWithShadow(cornerRadius: CGFloat, shadowColor: UIColor, shadowOpacity: Float, shadowOffset: CGSize, shadowRadius: CGFloat) {
           self.layer.cornerRadius = cornerRadius
           self.layer.masksToBounds = false
           self.layer.shadowColor = shadowColor.cgColor
           self.layer.shadowOpacity = shadowOpacity
           self.layer.shadowOffset = shadowOffset
           self.layer.shadowRadius = shadowRadius
           self.layer.shadowPath = UIBezierPath(roundedRect: self.bounds, cornerRadius: cornerRadius).cgPath
       }

// MARK: - Implementation Details

private func objectFromJSON<T>(at path: String) -> T {
  guard let url = getBundle().url(forResource: path, withExtension: nil),
    let json = try? JSONSerialization.jsonObject(with: Data(contentsOf: url), options: []),
    let result = json as? T else {
    fatalError("Unable to load JSON at path: \(path)")
  }
  return result
}

private struct JSONDocument {
  let data: [String: Any]

  init(path: String) {
    self.data = objectFromJSON(at: path)
  }

  subscript<T>(key: String) -> T {
    guard let result = data[key] as? T else {
      fatalError("Property '\(key)' is not of type \(T.self)")
    }
    return result
  }
}

// MARK: - Implementation Details

public struct File {
  public let name: String
  public let ext: String?
  public let relativePath: String
  public let mimeType: String

  public var url: URL {
    return url(locale: nil)
  }

  public func url(locale: Locale?) -> URL {
    let bundle = getBundle()
    let url = bundle.url(
      forResource: name,
      withExtension: ext,
      subdirectory: relativePath,
      localization: locale?.identifier
    )
    guard let result = url else {
      let file = name + (ext.flatMap { ".\($0)" } ?? "")
      fatalError("Could not locate file named \(file)")
    }
    return result
  }

  public var path: String {
    return path(locale: nil)
  }

  public func path(locale: Locale?) -> String {
    return url(locale: locale).path
  }
}

// MARK: - Implementation Details

private func objectFromJSON<T>(at path: String) -> T {
  guard let url = getBundle().url(forResource: path, withExtension: nil),
    let json = try? JSONSerialization.jsonObject(with: Data(contentsOf: url), options: []),
    let result = json as? T else {
    fatalError("Unable to load JSON at path: \(path)")
  }
  return result
}

private struct JSONDocument {
  let data: [String: Any]

  init(path: String) {
    self.data = objectFromJSON(at: path)
  }

  subscript<T>(key: String) -> T {
    guard let result = data[key] as? T else {
      fatalError("Property '\(key)' is not of type \(T.self)")
    }
    return result
  }
}

// swiftlint:enable explicit_type_interface identifier_name
// swiftlint:enable nesting type_body_length type_name vertical_whitespace_opening_braces

// MARK: - Implementation Details

public struct File {
  public let name: String
  public let ext: String?
  public let relativePath: String
  public let mimeType: String

  public var url: URL {
    return url(locale: nil)
  }

  public func url(locale: Locale?) -> URL {
    let bundle = getBundle()
    let url = bundle.url(
      forResource: name,
      withExtension: ext,
      subdirectory: relativePath,
      localization: locale?.identifier
    )
    guard let result = url else {
      let file = name + (ext.flatMap { ".\($0)" } ?? "")
      fatalError("Could not locate file named \(file)")
    }
    return result
  }

  public var path: String {
    return path(locale: nil)
  }

  public func path(locale: Locale?) -> String {
    return url(locale: locale).path
  }
}

// swiftlint:enable identifier_name line_length type_body_length

// MARK: - Implementation Details

private func objectFromJSON<T>(at path: String) -> T {
  guard let url = getBundle().url(forResource: path, withExtension: nil),
    let json = try? JSONSerialization.jsonObject(with: Data(contentsOf: url), options: []),
    let result = json as? T else {
    fatalError("Unable to load JSON at path: \(path)")
  }
  return result
}

private struct JSONDocument {
  let data: [String: Any]

  init(path: String) {
    self.data = objectFromJSON(at: path)
  }

  subscript<T>(key: String) -> T {
    guard let result = data[key] as? T else {
      fatalError("Property '\(key)' is not of type \(T.self)")
    }
    return result
  }
}

// MARK: - Implementation Details

public struct File {
  public let name: String
  public let ext: String?
  public let relativePath: String
  public let mimeType: String

  public var url: URL {
    return url(locale: nil)
  }

  public func url(locale: Locale?) -> URL {
    let bundle = getBundle()
    let url = bundle.url(
      forResource: name,
      withExtension: ext,
      subdirectory: relativePath,
      localization: locale?.identifier
    )
    guard let result = url else {
      let file = name + (ext.flatMap { ".\($0)" } ?? "")
      fatalError("Could not locate file named \(file)")
    }
    return result
  }

  public var path: String {
    return path(locale: nil)
  }

  public func path(locale: Locale?) -> String {
    return url(locale: locale).path
  }
}

struct CornerRadii {
    var topLeft: CGFloat = 0
    var topRight: CGFloat = 0
    var bottomLeft: CGFloat = 0
    var bottomRight: CGFloat = 0
    public init(topLeft: CGFloat, topRight: CGFloat, bottomLeft: CGFloat, bottomRight: CGFloat) {
        self.topLeft = topLeft
        self.topRight = topRight
        self.bottomLeft = bottomLeft
        self.bottomRight = bottomRight
    }
}

AITKit/AITKit/Classes/Src/UIView+Extension.swift (Line 48:9 - Line 82:2), AITSwiftPlatformModule/AITSwiftPlatformModule/Classes/Src/Util/Extension/UIView+Extension.swift (Line 192:9 - Line 227:5)

}
    }

    // 切圆角函数绘制线条
    func createPathWithRoundedRect(bounds: CGRect, cornerRadii: CornerRadii) -> CGPath {
        let minX = bounds.minX
        let minY = bounds.minY
        let maxX = bounds.maxX
        let maxY = bounds.maxY

        let topLeftCenterX = minX + cornerRadii.topLeft
        let topLeftCenterY = minY + cornerRadii.topLeft

        let topRightCenterX = maxX - cornerRadii.topRight
        let topRightCenterY = minY + cornerRadii.topRight

        let bottomLeftCenterX = minX + cornerRadii.bottomLeft
        let bottomLeftCenterY = maxY - cornerRadii.bottomLeft

        let bottomRightCenterX = maxX - cornerRadii.bottomRight
        let bottomRightCenterY = maxY - cornerRadii.bottomRight

        let path = CGMutablePath()
        // 顶左
        path.addArc(center: CGPoint(x: topLeftCenterX, y: topLeftCenterY), radius: cornerRadii.topLeft, startAngle: CGFloat.pi, endAngle: CGFloat.pi * 3 / 2, clockwise: false)
        // 顶右
        path.addArc(center: CGPoint(x: topRightCenterX, y: topRightCenterY), radius: cornerRadii.topRight, startAngle: CGFloat.pi * 3 / 2, endAngle: 0, clockwise: false)
        // 底右
        path.addArc(center: CGPoint(x: bottomRightCenterX, y: bottomRightCenterY), radius: cornerRadii.bottomRight, startAngle: 0, endAngle: CGFloat.pi / 2, clockwise: false)
        // 底左
        path.addArc(center: CGPoint(x: bottomLeftCenterX, y: bottomLeftCenterY), radius: cornerRadii.bottomLeft, startAngle: CGFloat.pi / 2, endAngle: CGFloat.pi, clockwise: false)
        path.closeSubpath()
        return path
    }
}

        let resetOrientationTarget = NSNumber(value: UIInterfaceOrientation.unknown.rawValue)
        UIDevice.current.setValue(resetOrientationTarget, forKey: "orientation")

        let orientationTarget = NSNumber(value: interfaceOrientation.rawValue)
        UIDevice.current.setValue(orientationTarget, forKey: "orientation")

        UIViewController.attemptRotationToDeviceOrientation()
    }
}

public struct ImageAsset {
  public fileprivate(set) var name: String

  public var image: AssetImageTypeAlias {
    let bundle = getBundle()
    #if os(iOS) || os(tvOS)
    let image = AssetImageTypeAlias(named: name, in: bundle, compatibleWith: nil)
    #elseif os(OSX)
    let image = bundle.image(forResource: NSImage.Name(name))
    #elseif os(watchOS)
    let image = AssetImageTypeAlias(named: name)
    #endif
    guard let result = image else { fatalError("Unable to load image named \(name).") }
    return result
  }
}

// swiftlint:enable identifier_name line_length type_body_length

// MARK: - Implementation Details

private func objectFromJSON<T>(at path: String) -> T {
  guard let url = getBundle().url(forResource: path, withExtension: nil),
    let json = try? JSONSerialization.jsonObject(with: Data(contentsOf: url), options: []),
    let result = json as? T else {
    fatalError("Unable to load JSON at path: \(path)")
  }
  return result
}

private struct JSONDocument {
  let data: [String: Any]

  init(path: String) {
    self.data = objectFromJSON(at: path)
  }

  subscript<T>(key: String) -> T {
    guard let result = data[key] as? T else {
      fatalError("Property '\(key)' is not of type \(T.self)")
    }
    return result
  }
}

// MARK: - Implementation Details

public struct File {
  public let name: String
  public let ext: String?
  public let relativePath: String
  public let mimeType: String

  public var url: URL {
    return url(locale: nil)
  }

  public func url(locale: Locale?) -> URL {
    let bundle = getBundle()
    let url = bundle.url(
      forResource: name,
      withExtension: ext,
      subdirectory: relativePath,
      localization: locale?.identifier
    )
    guard let result = url else {
      let file = name + (ext.flatMap { ".\($0)" } ?? "")
      fatalError("Could not locate file named \(file)")
    }
    return result
  }

  public var path: String {
    return path(locale: nil)
  }

  public func path(locale: Locale?) -> String {
    return url(locale: locale).path
  }
}

AITFoundation/AITFoundation/Classes/FoundationExts/ArrayExts.swift (Line 38:2 - Line 47:7), AITFoundation/AITFoundation/Classes/FoundationExts/DictionaryExts.swift (Line 10:2 - Line 19:74)

{
  func jsonString(prettify: Bool = false) -> String? {
    guard JSONSerialization.isValidJSONObject(self) else { return nil }
    let options = (prettify == true) ? JSONSerialization.WritingOptions.prettyPrinted : JSONSerialization.WritingOptions()
    guard let jsonData = try? JSONSerialization.data(withJSONObject: self, options: options) else { return nil }
    return String(data: jsonData, encoding: .utf8)
  }
}

private func objectFromJSON<T>(at path: String) -> T {
  guard let url = getBundle().url(forResource: path, withExtension: nil),
    let json = try? JSONSerialization.jsonObject(with: Data(contentsOf: url), options: []),
    let result = json as? T else {
    fatalError("Unable to load JSON at path: \(path)")
  }
  return result
}

private struct JSONDocument {
  let data: [String: Any]

  init(path: String) {
    self.data = objectFromJSON(at: path)
  }

  subscript<T>(key: String) -> T {
    guard let result = data[key] as? T else {
      fatalError("Property '\(key)' is not of type \(T.self)")
    }
    return result
  }
}

// MARK: - Implementation Details

public struct File {
  public let name: String
  public let ext: String?
  public let relativePath: String
  public let mimeType: String

  public var url: URL {
    return url(locale: nil)
  }

  public func url(locale: Locale?) -> URL {
    let bundle = getBundle()
    let url = bundle.url(
      forResource: name,
      withExtension: ext,
      subdirectory: relativePath,
      localization: locale?.identifier
    )
    guard let result = url else {
      let file = name + (ext.flatMap { ".\($0)" } ?? "")
      fatalError("Could not locate file named \(file)")
    }
    return result
  }

  public var path: String {
    return path(locale: nil)
  }

  public func path(locale: Locale?) -> String {
    return url(locale: locale).path
  }
}

AITRouterModule/AITRouterModule/Classes/AITRouterModuleService.swift (Line 39:14 - Line 230:2), AITSwiftPlatformModule/AITSwiftPlatformModule/Classes/Src/Network/HLMJSONAdapter.swift (Line 12:15 - Line 203:2)

: JSONAdapter {
    public init() {}

    // 返回未发现值的错误
    public func notFoundValueError(_ type: Any.Type, codingPath: [CodingKey]) -> DecodingError {
        return DecodingError.valueNotFound(type,
                                           DecodingError.Context(codingPath: codingPath,
                                                                 debugDescription: "Type dismatch, Expected \(type) value."))
    }

    // Int浮点、字符串转换
    public func adapt(_ decoder: CleanDecoder) throws -> Int {
        guard let res: Int = try adaptIfPresent(decoder) else {
            throw notFoundValueError(Int.self, codingPath: decoder.codingPath)
        }
        return res
    }

    // Int32浮点、字符串转换
    public func adapt(_ decoder: CleanDecoder) throws -> Int32 {
        guard let res: Int32 = try adaptIfPresent(decoder) else {
            throw notFoundValueError(Int32.self, codingPath: decoder.codingPath)
        }
        return res
    }

    // Int64浮点、字符串转换
    public func adapt(_ decoder: CleanDecoder) throws -> Int64 {
        guard let res: Int64 = try adaptIfPresent(decoder) else {
            throw notFoundValueError(Int64.self, codingPath: decoder.codingPath)
        }
        return res
    }

    // UInt浮点、字符串转换
    public func adapt(_ decoder: CleanDecoder) throws -> UInt {
        guard let res: UInt = try adaptIfPresent(decoder) else {
            throw notFoundValueError(UInt.self, codingPath: decoder.codingPath)
        }
        return res
    }

    // Float转化
    public func adapt(_ decoder: CleanDecoder) throws -> Float {
        guard let res: Float = try adaptIfPresent(decoder) else {
            throw notFoundValueError(Float.self, codingPath: decoder.codingPath)
        }
        return res
    }

    // Double转化
    public func adapt(_ decoder: CleanDecoder) throws -> Double {
        guard let res: Double = try adaptIfPresent(decoder) else {
            throw notFoundValueError(Double.self, codingPath: decoder.codingPath)
        }
        return res
    }

    // String转化
    public func adapt(_ decoder: CleanDecoder) throws -> String {
        guard let res: String = try adaptIfPresent(decoder) else {
            throw notFoundValueError(String.self, codingPath: decoder.codingPath)
        }
        return res
    }

    // Bool转化
    public func adapt(_ decoder: CleanDecoder) throws -> Bool {
        guard let res: Bool = try adaptIfPresent(decoder) else {
            throw notFoundValueError(Bool.self, codingPath: decoder.codingPath)
        }
        return res
    }

    // 日期为 null 或者类型不匹配时使用当前时间(支持字符串类型的时间)
    public func adapt(_ decoder: CleanDecoder) throws -> Date {
        guard let res: Date = try adaptIfPresent(decoder) else {
            throw notFoundValueError(Date.self, codingPath: decoder.codingPath)
        }
        return res
    }

    public func adaptIfPresent(_ decoder: CleanDecoder) throws -> Int? {
        guard !decoder.decodeNil() else { return nil }

        if let stringValue = try decoder.decodeIfPresent(String.self) {
            return Int(stringValue)
        }

        return nil
    }

    public func adaptIfPresent(_ decoder: CleanDecoder) throws -> Int32? {
        guard !decoder.decodeNil() else { return nil }

        if let stringValue = try decoder.decodeIfPresent(String.self) {
            return Int32(stringValue)
        }

        return nil
    }

    public func adaptIfPresent(_ decoder: CleanDecoder) throws -> Int64? {
        guard !decoder.decodeNil() else { return nil }

        if let stringValue = try decoder.decodeIfPresent(String.self) {
            return Int64(stringValue)
        }

        return nil
    }

    public func adaptIfPresent(_ decoder: CleanDecoder) throws -> UInt? {
        guard !decoder.decodeNil() else { return nil }

        if let stringValue = try decoder.decodeIfPresent(String.self) {
            return UInt(stringValue)
        }

        return nil
    }

    // float 字符串型、整型
    public func adaptIfPresent(_ decoder: CleanDecoder) throws -> Float? {
        guard !decoder.decodeNil() else { return nil }

        guard let stringValue = try decoder.decodeIfPresent(String.self) else {
            return nil
        }

        return Float(stringValue)
    }

    // double 字符串型、整型
    public func adaptIfPresent(_ decoder: CleanDecoder) throws -> Double? {
        guard !decoder.decodeNil() else { return nil }

        guard let stringValue = try decoder.decodeIfPresent(String.self) else {
            return nil
        }

        return Double(stringValue)
    }

    // String 字符串型、整型(必选类型默认实现已经支持转换)
    public func adaptIfPresent(_ decoder: CleanDecoder) throws -> String? {
        guard !decoder.decodeNil() else { return nil }

        if let intValue = try decoder.decodeIfPresent(Int.self) {
            return String(intValue)
        } else if let doubleValue = try decoder.decodeIfPresent(Double.self) {
            return String(doubleValue)
        } else if let boolValue = try decoder.decodeIfPresent(Bool.self) {
            return String(boolValue)
        }

        return nil
    }

    // 由于 Swift 布尔类型不是非 0 即 true，所以默认没有提供类型转换。
    // 如果想实现 Int 转 Bool 可以自定义解码。
    public func adaptIfPresent(_ decoder: CleanDecoder) throws -> Bool? {
        if let intValue = try decoder.decodeIfPresent(Int.self) {
            // 类型不匹配，期望 Bool 类型，实际是 Int 类型
            return intValue != 0
        }
        
        if let stringValue = try decoder.decodeIfPresent(String.self) {
            if stringValue == "true" {
                return true
            } else if stringValue == "false" {
                return false
            }
        }
        
        return nil
    }

    public func adaptIfPresent(_ decoder: CleanDecoder) throws -> Date? {
        guard !decoder.decodeNil() else { return nil }

        if let stringValue = try decoder.decodeIfPresent(String.self), let time = Double(stringValue), time > 0 {
            return Date(timeIntervalSince1970: time)
        }
        return nil
    }

//    // 可选的 URL 类型解析失败的时候返回一个默认 url
//    func adaptIfPresent(_ decoder: CleanDecoder) throws -> URL? {
//        return URL(string: "https://google.com")
//    }
}
